{"tid":564967,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港爆滿要返珠海酒店住　中國團友赤口狂罵導遊","createTime":"2018-02-18T13:58:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T19:22:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":35,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"42ade9902534771e13f7d9ab45ff93fb3eba4979","tid":564967,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T13:58:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180218/photo/bkn-20180218172019646-0218_00822_001_01p.jpg?20180218190448\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180218%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180218172019646-0218_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20180218190448&h=a6ea6c38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地團旅客初三狂鬧導遊「應節」。下午3時許，警方接獲一名姓洪(54歲)內地女子報案，指在尖沙咀華懋廣場對開有人打架，警員到場後，發現現場有約20人，屬於一個內地旅行團，當中約3名團友疑不滿未獲提供香港的酒店住宿，需要改住珠海的酒店，與2名分別姓姜(39歲)及姓黃(45歲)的女導遊發生爭執。導遊隨後聯絡公司，特別安排該3名團友入住香港的酒店，惟有人仍不滿旅行社未有安排交通，繼續大吵大鬧，3人其後獲安排接送服務，其餘團友則登上旅遊巴前往珠海的酒店，事件始告結束。警方列糾紛案處理。<br />\n<br />\n現場消息指，該內地旅行團團友來自國內多個省份，在深圳參加一個費用1100港元的參觀港珠澳大橋5天團，今日為行程第4天。而過去數日該旅行團均下榻青衣一間酒店，惟因農曆新年假期酒店房間爆滿，今晚未能繼續入住，需改住珠海的酒店。而根據該旅行團章程列明，若香港酒店爆滿，團友或可能需改住賓館或內地酒店。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180218/bkn-20180218172019646-0218_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180218%2Fbkn-20180218172019646-0218_00822_001.html&d=wKGJgGynjm6lP3PkoXFXv8mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=8fd8b1ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180218/bkn-20180218172019646-0218_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"1d1cc542b7ef4e43f110c06e2b14d6c53d54a4a1","tid":564967,"uid":166663,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T14:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.jiemeng8.com/article/UploadPic/2014-4/201441316131217046.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.jiemeng8.com%2Farticle%2FUploadPic%2F2014-4%2F201441316131217046.jpg&h=2ced5d29&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0e9a1a692debb2894040e8ad67365a8dccf7778b","tid":564967,"uid":54516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T14:09:15.000Z","msg":"華懋廣場平日下午好撚多支那人,阻撚住條路,唔屌鳩佢哋都唔會讓路."},{"pid":"f67ae1ff61edc591508cf67a040357596ab277f6","tid":564967,"uid":115585,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T14:26:09.000Z","msg":"1100蚊想包食包住酒店5日都已經夠古怪"},{"pid":"6cb2ae62785d13de514c39fea645800cd37ceff9","tid":564967,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T14:28:22.000Z","msg":"係唔係買唔夠數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c75d170eda4c68eebac36105dbf949ecd4f1da","tid":564967,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T14:28:33.000Z","msg":"車返去珠海都唔平"},{"pid":"fd869c01053c5b6066e431d1bada1138a8a4d026","tid":564967,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T14:44:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">而根據該旅行團章程列明，若香港酒店爆滿，團友或可能需改住賓館或內地酒店。</span>"},{"pid":"629682eca1db8e3ab165556050bc747785d08f91","tid":564967,"uid":117200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T14:47:17.000Z","msg":"打得好呀！班香港導遊都係黎r香港身份証嘅大陸人"},{"pid":"0d82393ec5704c83a8f8e360a436ce34c89ee18f","tid":564967,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T14:57:50.000Z","msg":"參觀港珠澳大橋5天團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f5664dc4b357fed415a0c535a5124d571b85c3","tid":564967,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f67ae1ff61edc591508cf67a040357596ab277f6","tid":564967,"uid":115585,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T14:26:09.000Z","msg":"1100蚊想包食包住酒店5日都已經夠古怪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T14:58:46.000Z","msg":"咪又係果d購物團，尖東大把依d場比大陸人買野"},{"pid":"517ee5b3ea4a1b173743e9d380b9fc1625e43497","tid":564967,"uid":26451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T15:03:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{